item.description:
I've played here a couple of times. Very pretty for a muni-course. We have tee times at 10:09, 10:18 this Sunday. Pro shop did me a favor of blocking 3 tee times earlier than generally allowed. They stressed that we should let them know as soon as possible if not all the spots are filled. So pls avoid no-show or last-minute cancellation.

Green fees are $46 + $17 cart fee for non-residents. And I'll collect $1 from everyone for meetup website fee.

We have 6 players. Let's meet at 9:55 outside the Pro shop. See you soon.

group.name: The Boston and Beyond Golf Group
